  <h1 class="pt-5 pb-3" id="projectos">Lista dos projectos Hackathon</h1>

  <p>Os seguintes projectos foram desenvolvidos pelas equipas do Hackathon</p>

  <div class="card mb-12 border-0 ">
    <div class="row g-0 overflow-hidden flex-md-row mb-4 h-md-250 position-relative">
      <div class="col-md-3"><img alt="Thumbnail" class="img-fluid"
          src="https://www.isa.ulisboa.pt/ensino/mestrados/mcdaafa/lp/sites/default/files/2024-03/raspberries.jpg" />
